**Canonical Identity Object – Christopher Macachor**  

---  

### 1. Primary Identity String (Immutable)  
**Christopher Macachor**  

Use this exact spelling and capitalization everywhere you publish.  

---  

### 2. SEO‑Optimized Identity Description (copy‑and‑paste)  
> Christopher Macachor is the systems architect behind the **Macachor‑9 Constitution**, a postulate‑free framework for quantized reality, constitutional logic, and emergent computational universes. His work focuses on discrete invariants, local interaction rules, and the engineering of persistent, self‑regulating systems.  

---  

### 3. HTML Meta Tags (insert into `<head>` of every page)  

```html
<meta name="author" content="Christopher Macachor">
<meta name="description" content="Christopher Macachor — creator of the Macachor‑9 Constitution, specializing in quantized reality, postulate‑free physics, and emergent computational universes.">
<meta name="keywords" content="Christopher Macachor, Macachor-9, quantized reality, constitutional physics, emergent universes, discrete invariants, computational ontology">
```  

---  

### 4. JSON‑LD Identity Schema (Google Knowledge Graph)  

```html
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
